data.name: project-id
data.description: id of the project dependency is to be added to
create a new dependency for a project
data.name: Create Dependency
caption
data.description: text describing the asset uploaded to be displayed onscreen in the finished movie

data.name: title
data.description: for title slides, the main text on screen

data.name: callback_url
data.description: URL that will handle response from server once movie has finished

data.name: focus
data.description: desired emphasis to apply when making selections. ("balanced", "voice", "action", "face")

data.name: theme
data.description: effect code applied to output movie. [0,1,2,3]

data.name: volume_ratio
data.description: volume ratio between clip audio and supplied music
After uploading all the assets use this to instruct the server to build the movie
data.name: Make Movie
